---
import LayoutB from '../../layouts/LayoutB.astro';
---

<LayoutB title="Home" description="Pear Tree Community School — Social justice Montessori education in Oakland, CA. 90% of students exceed literacy benchmarks.">

  <!-- Hero: Full-bleed editorial -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/images/hero-students.jpg`} alt="Students at play" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-black/80 via-black/50 to-transparent"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-32">
      <p class="text-amber-400 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-8">Oakland, California &middot; Est. 2012</p>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black text-white leading-[0.9] max-w-4xl mb-8" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">
        A new world<br />requires a new<br />way of <em class="italic">learning.</em>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-neutral-300 max-w-lg mb-12 leading-relaxed">
        Social justice Montessori education where 90% of students exceed literacy benchmarks — and no family is turned away.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/admissions`} class="px-8 py-4 bg-white text-neutral-900 font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-neutral-100 transition-colors">Schedule a Tour</a>
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/support`} class="px-8 py-4 border-2 border-white/30 text-white font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">Support Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats: Large editorial numbers -->
  <section class="bg-neutral-900 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
      <div>
        <p class="text-7xl font-black text-amber-400" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">90%</p>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 mt-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Exceed literacy benchmarks</p>
        <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm mt-2">While only 22% of Black and Latino students nationally reach proficiency.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-7xl font-black text-amber-400" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">80%</p>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 mt-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Receive financial aid</p>
        <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm mt-2">We believe access to excellent education is a right, not a privilege.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-7xl font-black text-amber-400" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">95%</p>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 mt-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Students of color</p>
        <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm mt-2">A school that reflects and centers the communities it serves.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission: Magazine editorial -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-neutral-400 mb-6">Our Mission</p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black leading-tight mb-8" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">
          Education for <em class="italic">liberation.</em>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Our decolonial Montessori curriculum centers Black, Indigenous, and students of color — not as an afterthought, but as the foundation of everything we teach.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Founded by Michele Hamilton, a trailblazing educator from East Oakland with 27+ years of experience, Pear Tree is both a model school and a training site for educational policy development.
        </p>
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/about`} class="text-neutral-900 font-bold border-b-2 border-neutral-900 pb-1 hover:text-neutral-600 hover:border-neutral-600 transition-colors">
          Read our story &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="relative">
        <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/images/montessori-classroom.jpg`} alt="Montessori math lesson" class="w-full rounded-2xl" />
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-amber-400 text-neutral-900 px-6 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-sm">
          Featured in London Review of Education
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Four Pillars: Dramatic cards -->
  <section class="bg-neutral-50 py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-neutral-400 mb-4 text-center">Academic Framework</p>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-center mb-6" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">Four Pillars of Excellence</h2>
      <p class="text-center text-neutral-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
        PTCS supports young people in becoming producers of academic and cultural content and critical thinkers of cultural and academic consumption.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-emerald-900 text-white rounded-2xl p-10 hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform">
          <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-300 mb-4">01</p>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">Social Justice &amp; Civic Engagement</h3>
          <p class="text-emerald-200 leading-relaxed">
            An historical-based curriculum engaging a deep sense of self and connection to ancestral contributions in mathematics, literature, philosophy, sciences and the arts.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-orange-600 text-white rounded-2xl p-10 hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform">
          <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-orange-200 mb-4">02</p>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">Cultural Art Enrichments</h3>
          <p class="text-orange-100 leading-relaxed">
            Expressive arts rooted in the traditions of the students we serve — deepening connections, addressing historical trauma, and supporting agency through creation and performance.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-amber-500 text-neutral-900 rounded-2xl p-10 hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform">
          <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-amber-800 mb-4">03</p>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">Rigorous Academics</h3>
          <p class="text-amber-900 leading-relaxed">
            Montessori-aligned content to deepen independence, strengthen writing, engage with mathematics as creative expression, and navigate the sciences with wonder and awe.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-blue-700 text-white rounded-2xl p-10 hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform">
          <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-blue-200 mb-4">04</p>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">Social &amp; Emotional Learning</h3>
          <p class="text-blue-100 leading-relaxed">
            Intentional curriculum to deepen peer community, knowledge of self, emotional literacy, and the ability to navigate social dynamics with thoughtfulness and intention.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Photo essay strip -->
  <section class="py-4 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="flex gap-4 px-4">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-80 h-64 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/images/homepage-1.jpg`} alt="Art gallery" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      </div>
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-80 h-64 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/images/classroom-photo.jpg`} alt="Classroom" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      </div>
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-80 h-64 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/images/early-days.jpg`} alt="Field trip" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      </div>
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-80 h-64 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/images/enrichment-performance.jpg`} alt="Cultural learning" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      </div>
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-80 h-64 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/images/homepage-3.jpg`} alt="Students collaborating" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Programs -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/programs#preschool`} class="group relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden aspect-[4/3]">
        <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/images/classroom-photo.jpg`} alt="Preschool" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/20 to-transparent"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-8">
          <p class="text-amber-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Ages 2+</p>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-white" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">Preschool</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-300 text-sm mt-2">Dragonfly &amp; Butterfly Classrooms</p>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/programs#elementary`} class="group relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden aspect-[4/3]">
        <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/images/montessori-classroom.jpg`} alt="Elementary" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/20 to-transparent"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-8">
          <p class="text-amber-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">TK &ndash; 5th Grade</p>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-white" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">Elementary</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-300 text-sm mt-2">Hummingbird, Falcon &amp; Dolphin Classrooms</p>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonial: Large editorial quote -->
  <section class="bg-neutral-900 text-white py-24">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-amber-400 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-8">What parents say</p>
      <blockquote>
        <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold leading-snug italic" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">
          "The thoughtfulness, creativity and love of the teachers — staff really 'see' each child and support healthy peer relationships."
        </p>
        <footer class="mt-8 text-neutral-500 text-sm">&mdash; Pear Tree Parent, via Berkeley Parents Network</footer>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Enrichments -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-neutral-400 mb-4">Beyond the Classroom</p>
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-black mb-12" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">Enrichments &amp; Field Trips</h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">Sound Recording &amp; Video</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
          Students create their own documentaries, video journals, and songs — becoming producers of content, not just consumers.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">Cultural Arts</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
          Art, music, dance, Capoeira, Spanish, and gardening — in partnership with The People's Conservatory.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">Educational Journeys</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
          Curriculum-aligned trips to Chabot Space Center, Oakland Museum, UC Berkeley Botanical Garden, and multi-day cultural immersions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="relative py-32">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/images/homepage-1.jpg`} alt="Community" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/70"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white mb-6" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">
        Join our <em class="italic">community.</em>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-neutral-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
        Whether you're looking for a school that sees your child, or you want to invest in education that transforms — there's a place for you here.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/admissions`} class="px-8 py-4 bg-white text-neutral-900 font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-neutral-100 transition-colors">Schedule a Tour</a>
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/support`} class="px-8 py-4 bg-amber-400 text-neutral-900 font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-amber-300 transition-colors">Make a Gift</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</LayoutB>
